---
title: Cherry Tomato, Bacon & Basil Pizza with Pear Mixed Leaf Salad
description: Add extra flavour to your pizza by roasting the veggies first to ensure every bite is a tasty delight. Top the whole thing
with basil leaves for a fresh and fragrant flavour so you’ll never rely on takeaway again!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cherry-tomato-courgette-basil-pizza-58caaafa.jpg
